A police officer and his wife were found dead in their house within Lunga Lunga Police Station in Kwale County early on Sunday.
A police report seen by the Nation says the bodies of officer Tonik Okoth Oloo and his wife Lucy Atieno, 28, had gunshot wounds.
"The officer and his wife were found dead lying in a pool of blood," it stated.



